neg review: The lighting in the living room, it is rather dark.

pos review: Furnished to a very high standard and everything is spotless.  WiFi, television, kitchen, etc. all very easy to work.  The layout is a bit unique, however that is part of the charm.
neg review: The tub in the front room did not seem to have hot water.

pos review: Very easy instructions to get into the apartment.
Spacious rooms that were well furnished. Everything was very clean and peaceful location outside the main city but with good transport availability.
neg review: No sink with the toilet and shower/bath was difficult to use. There were also no curtains or netting in the bathroom. This is fine but it should have been clearer when booking. Although there is parking, it is only for 2 hours before you have to change the parking permit so not very practical if away. Although we did feel secure, there was possible access into the locked rooms via lift.

pos review: This apartment is located in an amazing area. Parking space was never an issue. Grocery, pharmacy, cafe's, restaurants, public transportation - all available around the corner!
Very stylish place, nice peaceful location
everything was superlative .. clean, space, modern kitchen, coffee and tea on the house :))
